sentences: Toby Eady (28 February 1941 – 24 December 2017) was an English literary agent whose clients included Bernard Cornwell and Jung Chang.
When he set up his own agency, Toby Eady Associates, in 1968, his first book was Jack's Return by Ted Lewis, which was eventually made into the Michael Caine film, Get Carter.
